org.jboss.aerogear.sync.server

Interface ServerSynchronizer<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of documents that this engine can handle.
    S - The type of Edits that this synchronizer can handle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiffMatchPatchServerSynchronizer, JsonMergePatchServerSynchronizer, JsonPatchServerSynchronizer

    public interface ServerSynchronizer<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>
    A instance of this class will be able to handle tasks needed to implement Differential Synchronization for a specific type of documents.
